skinset.Site.basic = Basic Layout|The basic skins used to display your site, eg. the main page, stylesheet, external javascript file etc.
skinset.Site.navigation = Navigation|Skins used for different navigation parts on your site.
skinset.Site.topics = Topics|The skins used to display topics.
skinset.Site.calendar = Calendar|The skins used for rendering the calendar.
skinset.Site.rss = RSS feed|The skins used for the RSS feed of this site.
skinset.Site.search = Search|All search (and search result) skins.
skinset.Site.referrers = Referrers|The skins used to display the referrers pointing to this site.
skinset.Site.mostread = Mostread stories|The skins involved in the &raquo;most read&laquo; section of your site.
skinset.Site.mails = Mails|The body of confirmation mails that are sent by Antville.
skinset.Site.preferences = Preference forms|Skins defining the layout of the site preferences page.
skinset.Site.user = Login, Registration and Subscriptions
skinset.Site.membermgr = Member management|All the skins used in the &raquo;members&laquo; section of a site.
skinset.Site.various = Various other skins
             
skinset.Story = Stories|All skins that are used to display stories in different contexts.
skinset.Story.basic = Basic Layout|The skins used for rendering the preview and the full display of stories.
skinset.Story.backlinks = Backlinks|All skins used for rendering the backlinks pointing to a story.
skinset.Story.editor = Story editor|The form for editing a story.
skinset.Story.list = Story pool|The skins used to display the &raquo;stories&laquo; section of the site.

skinset.Comment = Comments|Skins used to display comments and the form for entering a new or editing an existing comment.

skinset.Image = Images|This section contains all skins used for rendering images in your site.

skinset.File = Files|Skins used to display files in your site.

skinset.Poll = Polls|Skins used for rendering polls and their results.
skinset.Poll.basic = Basic Layout
skinset.Poll.editor = Editor forms
skinset.Poll.list = List of polls|These skins control the layout of the poll listing in the &raquo;polls&laquo; section of the site.

