##
## skin explanation texts
##
## StoryMgr
skin.StoryMgr.main = Main page|The basic view of the &raquo;stories&laquo; section of a site.

## SysMgr
skin.SysMgr.list = Listing|This is the generic skin for all listings in the system manager.
skin.SysMgr.setup = System Setup|The form for the setup of an Antville installation.
skin.SysMgr.deletewarnmail = Delete Notification Mail|This is the mail message that is sent to site owners to tell them that their site is about to be deleted.
skin.SysMgr.sitesearchform = Site search form|This skin contains the form for searching sites in system manager.
skin.SysMgr.blockwarnmail = Block Notification Mail|This is the mail message that is sent to site owners to warn them that their site is about to be blocked.
skin.SysMgr.syslogsearchform = Log search form|The form for searching within the log entries of system manager.
skin.SysMgr.usersearchform = User search form|The form for searching users in the system manager.
skin.SysMgr.status = Status|Displays the system status information.

## Layout
skin.Layout.main = Layout overview|Displays a preview of a layout including links to the available options.
skin.Layout.download = Download page|Whenever a user wants to download a layout this skin will be rendered.
skin.Layout.chooserlistitem = Chooserlist item|This skin is used to display a layout in the chooser list (that is rendered after the user clicked on &raquo;choose a new layout&laquo;).
skin.Layout.testdrive = Testdrive message|Display the name of the layout that is currently tested (and a link to terminate the test). This skin will be shown in the message area of the page.
skin.Layout.mgrlistitem = List item|This skin is used to display a single layout in the list of existing layouts.
skin.Layout.edit = Layout editor|This is the form for editing a layout.

## ImageMgr
skin.ImageMgr.main = Image list|Displays the list of images in the &raquo;images&laquo; section of a site.
skin.ImageMgr.new = New image|This is the form for uploading a new image to the site's imagepool.

## Topic
skin.Topic.main = Main topic page|The skin for customizing the look of topic pages.
skin.Topic.imagetopic = Main gallery page|The skin that is used to display an image gallery.

## File
skin.File.main = File display|This skin defines the way files are displayed when embedded in a story or comment using the <% file %> macro.
skin.File.mgrlistitem = File list item|Displays a file in the &raquo;files&laquo; section of a site.
skin.File.edit = File editor|The form for editing an existing file.

## Choice
skin.Choice.main = Display|The form part for a single choice of a poll.
skin.Choice.result = Choice result|This skin defines the way a single choice result of a poll will be displayed.
skin.Choice.graph = Graph bar|The bar for visualizing the percentage of votes for a choice.
skin.Choice.edit = Choice editor|This is the form element for editing a single choice of a poll (used whenever a user is editing a poll).

## SkinMgr
skin.SkinMgr.main = Skin list|The main page body of the skin manager.
skin.SkinMgr.page = Main page|This is the main page that is used for the skin manager.
skin.SkinMgr.treebranch = Skin section|This skin is used to render a section of skins in the skinmanager.
skin.SkinMgr.new = New custom skin|Contains the form for creating a new custom skin.
skin.SkinMgr.treeleaf = Skin list item|Used to render a skin in the skinmanager.
skin.SkinMgr.edit = Skin editor|This is the form for editing a skin.

## Story
skin.Story.searchview = Search result view|This skin defines how a story or comment will be displayed in the list of search results.
skin.Story.display = Story display|Displays the contents of a story. By default it is embedded in the skins &raquo;Preview&laquo;, &raquo;Full story&laquo; and &raquo;Comment&laquo;.
skin.Story.rssResource = RSS resource|The &raquo;resource&laquo; part of a story in the site's RSS feed.
skin.Story.dayheader = Day header|Used to separate between different days in a list of stories (it is shown on top of the list of stories of a single day).
skin.Story.comment = Comment page|This skin defines the page containing the form for adding a new comment.
skin.Story.mgrlistitem = Item display|Displays a single story in the &raquo;stories&laquo; section of a site.
skin.Story.edit = Story editor form|This is the form used for creating a new or editing an existing story.
skin.Story.rssItem = RSS item|This skin is used to display a story in the RSS feed of a site.
skin.Story.historyview = &raquo;recently modified&laquo; item|This skin defines how both stories and comments appear in the list of recently modified items.
skin.Story.main = Full story view|This skin is used to display a story in the way you defined it in the &raquo;display&laquo; skin plus its comments.
skin.Story.embed = Embedded story view|This skin will be used to display a story when you embed it in a skin using the macro.
skin.Story.preview = Story preview|This skin is used to display a story on a front page (i.e. either the front page of your site or the front page of a single day).
skin.Story.backlinks = List of Backlinks|This skin is used whenever there are referrers pointing to a story.
skin.Story.mostread = &raquo;Mostread&laquo; display|Displays a single story in the list of &raquo;most read&laquo; stories of a site.
skin.Story.backlinkItem = Backlink|This skin is used to display a single backlink in the list of backlinks of a story.

## Comment
skin.Comment.reply = Reply|This skin defines how replies to comments are displayed.
skin.Comment.toplevel = Toplevel comment|Defines the layout of top-level comments to a story.
skin.Comment.edit = Comment editor|This skin contains the form for adding a top-level comment or reply.

## HopObject
skin.HopObject.delete = Delete confirmation|Displays a confirmation page whenever a user wants to delete something.

## Global
skin.Global.nextpagelink = Link to next page|This skin displays a link to older entries. It's used in all item lists (i.e. in the story, image, file manager), in topics and for site navigation if you include it in the main page.
skin.Global.colorpicker = Color picker|Displays the small version of the color picker (without sample area).
skin.Global.rssImage = RSS image|This skin is used to render a site image item in the RSS feed.
skin.Global.colorpickerExt = Color picker (extended)|Displays the extended version of the color picker (which also contains an area showing the selected colors used in an example text);
skin.Global.pagenavigationitem = Page navigation item|A single page inside the page navigation will be displayed using this skin.
skin.Global.pagenavigation = Page navigation bar|The main skin to display the page navigation bar.
skin.Global.prevpagelink = Link to previous page|This skin displays a link to newer entries. It's used in all item lists (i.e. in the story, image, file manager), in topics and for site navigation if you include it in the main page.
skin.Global.colorpickerScripts = Color picker script|This skin contains the client side javascript methods used in the color picker.
skin.Global.colorpickerWidget = Widget|This is the skin that displays a small box filled with a selected color (normally it's shown on the right of the form elements for entering a color code).

## LayoutImageMgr
skin.LayoutImageMgr.main = List of layout images|This skin contains the list of available images of a layout.
skin.LayoutImageMgr.new = New layout image|This is the form for uploading a new layout image.
skin.LayoutImageMgr.navigation = Additional navigation|This skin contains additional navigation links (eg. the link to the &raquo;standard images&laquo; of the basis layout). It will only be used if a layout is based on another one which owns images too.

## Image
skin.Image.main = Display in image list|This skin is used to display an image with its name and description in the &raquo;images&laquo; section of the site.
skin.Image.mgrlistitem = Image list item|The way an image is displayed in the &raquo;images&laquo; section of a site (and in the list of images of a layout).
skin.Image.edit = Image editor|The form for editing an already uploaded image.
skin.Image.preview = Image preview|Used to display a preview of an image.

## FileMgr
skin.FileMgr.main = File list|This skin contains the list of available files in the &raquo;files&laquo; section of the site.
skin.FileMgr.new = New file|The form for uploading a new file.

## SysLog
skin.SysLog.sysmgr_listitem = Log entry|Displays a single log entry in the log manager.

## LayoutImage
skin.LayoutImage.edit = Layout image editor|The form for editing an existing layout image.

## Poll
skin.Poll.main = Main display|This skin shows a poll as form for voting.
skin.Poll.mgrlistitem = Poll list item|This skin is used to display a single poll in the site's &raquo;polls&laquo; section.
skin.Poll.results = Result display|This skin shows the overall results of a poll.
skin.Poll.edit = Poll editor|The form for creating a new or editing an existing poll.

## LayoutMgr
skin.LayoutMgr.main = Layout list|This skin contains the list of available site layouts.
skin.LayoutMgr.new = New Layout|The form for creating a new layout.
skin.LayoutMgr.import = Import a layout|This is the form for importing a layout zip file.

## User
skin.User.subscriptions = Subscription list|This skin is used to display the subscriptions or memberships of a user.
skin.User.sysmgr_listitem = User display|Used to display a single user in the user list of system manager.
skin.User.edit = Profile editor|Contains the form used for changing the profile of a user.
skin.User.sysmgr_edit = User editor|This skin contains the form for editing a user in system manager.
skin.User.sitelist = List of subscribed sites|This skin contains the sites a user is subscribed to or a member of ordered by their last update.

## Day
skin.Day.main = Main page of a single day|Whenever a user selects a single day via the calendar, this skin will be used to display the list of stories of this day.

## Skin
skin.Skin.diffline = Diff line|Displays a single line of the skin source when in &raquo;diff&laquo; mode.
skin.Skin.statuscustom = Status of a custom skin|This skin contains the status information of a custom skin.
skin.Skin.status = Status of a modified skin|Displays the status of a standard skin that was modified (eg. containing the links to &raquo;diff&laquo; and &raquo;reset&laquo;).
