skin.Site.referrers = Site referrers|This skin contains the list of referrers linking to a site.
skin.Site.sysmgr_listitem = Site display|This skin is used to display a single site in the system manager's site list.
skin.Site.welcome = Welcome to new site|This is the basic welcome message for users who are not system administrators. This skin is used as long as a site doesn't contain any story.
skin.Site.welcomeowner = Welcome message for site owner|This skin contains some additions to the welcome message for the site owner.
skin.Site.rssItem = RSS item|This skin is used to display a site in the RSS feed of an Antville installation.
skin.Site.calendarselday = Selected day|Whenever a user views the stories of a specific day, this skin will be used to highlight the selected day.
skin.Site.page = Main page|This is the basic skin of your site. Changing this skin will affect the whole site.
