skin.Site.calendardayheader = Header|This skin defines the appearence of the calendar's column headers (i.e. the days &raquo;Mon&laquo;, &raquo;Tue&laquo;, etc.).
skin.Site.adminnavigation = Navigation bar for site administrators|This skin contains the additional navigation items for administrators (i.e. edit preferences, edit skins ...).

## Root
skin.Root.list = Site list|This skin contains the list of sites of an Antville installation.
skin.Root.rss = RSS feed|This is the main skin used to render the RSS feed containing the list of recently updated sites.
