skin.Root.style = Stylesheet|The external stylesheet used to display the basic view of an Antville installation.
skin.Root.new = Create a new site|This is the form for creating a new site.
skin.Root.sysmgrnavigation = Navigation bar for system administrators|This skin contains some navigation links for system administrators.
skin.Root.blocked = Blocked user|If a blocked user requests a page this skin will be rendered instead.
skin.Root.notfound = Notfound page|Displayed if a request ends in a 404 Not Found
skin.Root.sysError = System Error page|Displayed if a system error occurs.

